  "texts": [
    "Asia ChinaChina's use of AI in governance and surveillance has been a subject of considerable debate and criticism in the West.",
    "The country is often portrayed as compromising governance to enable security-focused AI applications.",
    "However, this view is an oversimplification.",
    "While stability remains a critical priority for the Chinese government, there is an evolving attitude within the country towards AI-enabled surveillance policies.",
    "The State Council of China has emphasized AI's \"irreplaceable role\" in maintaining stability, as evident in the AI-enabled social credit system based on exhaustive data gathering to incentivize compliance."
